reviewText: I really enjoyed this film... The relationship that Treasure had with her mother was unfortunately, not far from reality in some cases.  I thought the activities/events of prison life was really bold of HBO and I was impressed with their dedication to keep things in line with reality.  I think the acting in the film, especially by Treasure, was very well presented.  The characters were believable and realistic.  Great job on this one...
